    <item>
      <title>Re: Newbie Good Samaritans (AKA Ky's Chatter Box - 11/2/2004)</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=TNZ&amp;message.id=132821#M132821</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;Well, like said earlier in this thread, most on my server considered me a noob. I started to play in July of 2003 on Feninn Ro, a server a RL friend played on). I made a dwarf paladin, who is my main to this day. FR is an old server and there are barely any low level characters that aren't alts. When I was lvl 6 or 7, I fianlly adventured outside of Kaladim, and learned the meaning of "TRAIN". Needless to say, the&amp;nbsp;halfinlinf who trianed me apologized and helped me recover my corpse. He then told me to /follow, which took me 10 minutes to understand. He took me to a goblin camp and proceeded to buff me. Having never been buffed by anybody, I started to freak. He clamed me down and proceeded to tell me he was going to power level me. It had taken me a week to get this far. I slayed goblins and looted up. He asked that i give him any bronze that may drop, which i did. One hour later I was 3 levels higher and very satisfied with my new friend Xenocyde, a 64 druid. I added him to my friends list said thank you and logged for the night.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;The next night I logged in and started killing mobs in BB on my own again, and Xeno showed up. he gave me a hail and my trade window popped up with a full set of bronze armor and a Coldain Axe of the Frost. Apparently he was skilling up his b;acksmithing and instead of selling back the armor pieces he was helping the noobs in BB. I found out a week later that Xeno was a RL friend of the guy who got me into EQ. &lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Xeno's toon is still on the server, but the man that made the toon great, has since left EQ, I miss him and everyday if I see a low level toon, I help him out be it a buff, equipment or plat, I do what I can to carry on Xeno's legacy oof help.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Gimur DaTwink&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;62 Paladin of Brell Serelis&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Member of Platinum Dragons on Fennin Ro&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;Flagged for fire!!!&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
