      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;Reading some of the posts I come to remember another time when someone helped me out.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;I was in POK one night on my Shaman, at this time I was casting spells for donation so that I can practice my Alchemy Skill. A Higher level Pally came up to me and started to talk, I guess he liked the way the convo went, he asked for a few buffs with I gladly gave him and asked if he needed anything else. He said no but then asked what I was planning on doing, I told him I'm trying to practice Alchemy but low on PP. He asked if I could make SOW potions, I said sure how many would you want, he asked for three 10 doses and gave me 300P, I told him thats way to much for just three 10 doses. He said take it, consider it a donation to help you out.&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
